---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Configuration">
  <h1>Configuration Reference</h1>
  <p>
    EncodeSwarmr is configured via YAML files. The Controller and Agent each have their own configuration file.
  </p>

  <h2>Controller Configuration</h2>
  <p>Default location: <code>/etc/encodeswarmr/controller.yaml</code> or passed via <code>--config</code> flag.</p>

  <h3>Server</h3>
  <pre><code>server:
  http_addr: ":8080"        # REST API + Web UI listen address
  grpc_addr: ":9443"        # gRPC agent service listen address
  tls:
    cert: /path/to/cert.pem
    key: /path/to/key.pem
    ca: /path/to/ca.pem     # CA for mTLS agent verification</code></pre>

  <h3>Database</h3>
  <pre><code>database:
  host: localhost
  port: 5432
  name: encodeswarmr
  user: encodeswarmr
  password: changeme
  sslmode: prefer
  max_open_conns: 25
  max_idle_conns: 5</code></pre>

  <h3>Authentication</h3>
  <pre><code>auth:
  session_secret: "generate-a-secure-random-string"
  token_ttl: 24h
  oidc:
    enabled: false
    issuer: https://auth.example.com
    client_id: encodeswarmr
    client_secret: secret
    redirect_url: https://encodeswarmr.example.com/auth/callback
    role_claim: groups
    role_mapping:
      admin: encodeswarmr-admins
      operator: encodeswarmr-operators
      viewer: encodeswarmr-viewers</code></pre>

  <h3>Storage</h3>
  <pre><code>storage:
  media_paths:
    - /mnt/media/input
    - /mnt/media/output
  cloud:
    s3:
      bucket: my-encodes
      region: us-east-1
    gcs:
      bucket: my-encodes
    azure:
      container: my-encodes
      account: storageaccount</code></pre>

  <h3>Webhooks</h3>
  <pre><code>webhooks:
  - name: discord-notifications
    url: https://discord.com/api/webhooks/...
    provider: discord    # discord | teams | slack
    secret: hmac-secret  # HMAC-SHA256 signing key
    events:
      - job.completed
      - job.failed
      - agent.offline</code></pre>

  <h3>Rate Limiting</h3>
  <pre><code>rate_limit:
  requests_per_second: 200
  burst: 400</code></pre>

  <h2>Agent Configuration</h2>
  <p>Default location: <code>C:\ProgramData\EncodeSwarmr\agent.yaml</code> (Windows) or <code>/etc/encodeswarmr/agent.yaml</code> (Linux).</p>

  <pre><code>controller:
  address: "controller.example.com:9443"
  tls:
    cert: /path/to/agent-cert.pem
    key: /path/to/agent-key.pem
    ca: /path/to/ca.pem

agent:
  name: "encode-node-01"       # Display name in the UI
  work_dir: "C:\\Temp\\encodes" # Temporary working directory
  max_concurrent_jobs: 2       # Parallel job limit
  gpu:
    auto_detect: true          # Auto-detect GPU capabilities
    # Or specify manually:
    # type: nvenc
    # device: 0</code></pre>

  <h2>Environment Variables</h2>
  <p>All configuration values can be overridden via environment variables with the <code>ESWR_</code> prefix:</p>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Variable</th><th>Config Path</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>ESWR_DATABASE_HOST</code></td><td>database.host</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>ESWR_DATABASE_PASSWORD</code></td><td>database.password</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>ESWR_SERVER_HTTP_ADDR</code></td><td>server.http_addr</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>ESWR_AUTH_SESSION_SECRET</code></td><td>auth.session_secret</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

